<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Linux on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/tags/linux/</link><description>Recent content in Linux on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 21 Jan 2023 19:36:01 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/tags/linux/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>显示按键等信息</title><link>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%8C%89%E9%94%AE%E7%AD%89%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Jan 2023 19:36:01 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%8C%89%E9%94%AE%E7%AD%89%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF/</guid><description>&lt;p>在 Linux 系统中捕捉并显示按键等信息。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>睡眠、休眠与恢复</title><link>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E4%BC%91%E7%9C%A0%E4%B8%8E%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D/</link><pubDate>Thu, 19 Jan 2023 21:18:38 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E4%BC%91%E7%9C%A0%E4%B8%8E%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D/</guid><description>&lt;p>Linux 系统的&lt;em>休眠&lt;/em>（Hibernation）与&lt;em>恢复&lt;/em>（Resume）可能需要额外的设置才能生效。此外，笔记本上的 Linux 系统从&lt;em>睡眠&lt;/em>（Suspend）中恢复后，可能出现键盘（以及触摸板）无法使用的情况。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>逆转 Grub 菜单中的 Linux Kernel 顺序</title><link>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/%E9%80%86%E8%BD%AC-grub-%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84-linux-kernel-%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Nov 2022 00:22:02 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/%E9%80%86%E8%BD%AC-grub-%E8%8F%9C%E5%8D%95%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84-linux-kernel-%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F/</guid><description>&lt;p>当一个 Linux 系统（Arch Linux）上同时安装了多个 Kernel 时，貌似在 Grub 菜单中会将较新（指安装顺序，而不是版本顺序）的 Kernel 设置为默认内核。而现在要将较老的 Kernel 设置为默认。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Linux</title><link>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Nov 2022 00:14:14 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/record/linux/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>